<a href="/articles/26572.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26572/indexMediumPc2/26572.jpeg?1462763611" alt="「这世界」伦敦新市长出炉，人们最关心的是他的穆斯林身份">
		
